(16, 'oxford blucher black wax', 'black', 'Blucher is a type of shoes that made from a single piece of leather. Its simple and perfect for a very formal suit and tie occation. Made on our Italy last it tick another box as our Italy last are narrow shape on the toe.', 'M', 90),
